                <div class="kicker"><span class="kicker"><a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/section/news">NEWS</a></span></div>

                <h1>Research reveals impact of lax scandal on Duke&#039;s image</h1>
                
                
                                    <div class="row  mt-4 mb-0 mb-md-4">
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                            <aside class="author-name">
                                    
    
                                    
            By <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/adam-eaglin">Adam Eaglin</a>
                                    
                                <div class="mt-1">
                                    <span class="can-localize">September 27, 2006 | 12:00am EDT</span>
                                </div>
                            </aside>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 text-left text-md-right d-print-none">
                            <ul class="social-links list-unsyled list-inline mt-4 mt-md-0">
                                <li class="list-inline-item"><a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https://www.dukechronicle.com/article/2006/09/research-reveals-impact-lax-scandal-dukes-image" target="_blank" class="sends-events" data-ga-category="Share" data-ga-action="click" data-ga-label="facebook" data-ga-value="CURL"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a></li>
